---
title: Cal Smart Honey-Chipotle Turkey with Zesty Bulgur Salad
description: Sweet and spicy honey-chipotle sauce drizzled over smoky, seasoned turkey – tonight's lip-smacking supper is bringing flavour upon flavour! A zesty lime bulgur wheat salad adds texture and zip to every bite!

